Pre-Game Insights: Germany midfielder Aleksandar Pavlovic (20) will be back from injury for their Nations League match at home to Netherlands on Monday and will form a midfield partnership with Angelo Stiller (23), coach Julian Nagelsmann said on Sunday.
Germany, who drew 2-2 with the Dutch in Amsterdam in September, are top of Nations League Group A3 on seven points from three matches, with Netherlands second on five.
Others: Germany coach Julian Nagelsmann praised the pair as prospects for the team ahead of the 2026 World Cup.
For Stiller it would be his third cap, having made his international debut only last month.
